<BlogPost
  title="How to prepare any repo for AI coding tools in 2026"
  description="Your repo needs CLAUDE.md, .cursorrules, AGENTS.md, and GEMINI.md. Here is what goes in each, what they share, and how to maintain them without the files drifting apart."
  date="April 12, 2026"
